---
title: "Researchers - Drug Development with Repurposing Research"
description: "Use CureAccelerator to reach out to the repurposing community and find medial repurposing collaborators and potential funders."
---
<section role="banner" aria-label="repurposing-research" class="page-header header--green">
  <div class="header-content__container role-page">
    <div class="header-content__left">
      <%= image_tag 'roles/researcher-img-2.png', alt: 'Researchers', class: 'user-role-img' %>
    </div>
    <div class="header-content__right">
      <h6 class="title__inverse uppercase">Researchers</h6>
      <h3 class="title__inverse">Why Join CureAccelerator?</h3>
      <p class="title__inverse">Are you passionate about a therapeutic area, or an expert on a particular compound or device? With CureAccelerator, you can reach out to the repurposing community and find those who share your interests – potential funders, as well as potential collaborators.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Sign Up', ' https://app.cureaccelerator.org/registration', class: 'button button--white button--header' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= partial 'components/page-scroll' %>
</section>
<section class="callout--brown" role="region" aria-labelledby="about-cure-accelerator">
  <div class="callout--container">
    <blockquote class="text center">
      &ldquo;I believe that repositioning existing drugs for new diseases represents the most cost and time effective means to systematically deliver new treatments to patients in need. However, the business case for any single stakeholder remains challenging. CureAccelerator provides the essential coordination function, and ensures the unified focus to translate new drug-disease hypotheses, through clinical testing to patient care.&rdquo;
      <cite>Craig Webb, Chief Scientific Officer at NuMedii, Inc.</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>
<section role="region" aria-label="clinicians-features" id="page-scroll" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag">What can I do with CureAccelerator?</h6>
  </header>
  <div class="page-section--body">
    <h1 class="title" id="clinicians-features">Pursue repurposing research you care about to create change</h1>
    <p class="text">CureAccelerator’s community is composed of like-minded people who are dedicated to creating effective treatments through repurposing.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-layout">
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon ideas">Ideas</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Post repurposing research ideas</h5>
      <p>Do you think an existing drug, device or nutriceutical could be used in a new way to address an unmet need? The CureAccelerator community wants to know about it, including the CureAccelerator funding community.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon connect">Connect</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Connect with funders</h5>
      <p>Respond to current Requests for Proposals (RFPs), or receive funding pledges on your proposals. Through discussion boards and member connections, you can receive and provide feedback on the Proposals and RFPs of others.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon support">Support</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Find peer support</h5>
      <p>Locate peers around the world, at major institutions or in isolated labs, who are as passionate about repurposing as you are.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon global-2">Global</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Join a global community</h5>
      <p>CureAccelerator is the world’s first online, interactive platform dedicated to repurposing research – a repurposing hub for people, knowledge and resources to connect in service to patients. Welcome!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<hr class="page-section--divider">
<section role="region" aria-labelledby="featured-users" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag">CureAccelerator Community</h6>
  </header>
   <div class="page-section--body">
    <h2 class="title">Other User Roles</h2>
    <% link_to 'clinicians.html', class: 'card one-half shift hover' do %>
      <%= image_tag 'roles/clinician-img-2.png', alt: 'Clinicians', class: 'card--border__green-alt-1' %>
      <h5 class="card--title__green-alt-1">Clinicians</h5>
    <% end %>
    <% link_to 'funders.html', class: 'card one-half hover' do %>
      <%= image_tag 'roles/funders-img.png', alt: 'Funders', class: 'card--border__purple' %>
      <h5 class="card--title__purple">Funders</h5>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>